## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="51614-102">ASP.NET 页面可以存储<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>之间本质上是无状态的 HTTP 请求和响应处理，并为任何 Web 页面提供服务所需状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-102">ASP.NET pages can store <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> state between the inherently stateless HTTP request and response required to process and serve any Web page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-103">此状态称为"查看状态"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-103">This state is called "view state".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-104">用于存储为页及其控件的视图状态的默认机制是在一个或多个`<hidden>`从 Web 服务器提供给客户端页面中包含的 HTML 字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-104">The default mechanism used to store view state for a page and its controls is in one or more `<hidden>` HTML fields included in the page that is served to a client from a Web server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-105"><xref:System.Web.UI.Page>类可以使用<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister>类来执行此操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-105">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> class to do this work.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> 实现<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A>并<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A>方法的<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>类，以便<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>可以存储在状态`<hidden>`名为"__VIEWSTATE"Web 客户端上的 HTML 元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> class so that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> can store state in a `<hidden>` HTML element named "__VIEWSTATE" on a Web client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-107">当客户端请求从 Web 服务器 （回发） 时，相同的页面时`<hidden>`分析元素并将其转换为状态信息由 ASP.NET。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-107">When the client requests the same page from the Web server (a postback), the `<hidden>` element is parsed and converted to state information by ASP.NET.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="51614-108">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>请求的实例都有一个关联<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter>类，它将检索<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>此适配器使用的对象<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-108">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> instance that is requested has an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter> class, it retrieves the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object from this adapter using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-109">适配器可以重写<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A>方法以返回<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>特定客户端支持某种方式存储页面和控件状态的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-109">Adapters can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method to return a <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object that stores page and control state in some way that a specific client supports.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-110">例如，<xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister>类在 Web 服务器上，而不是客户端，若要减少的信息，必须发送并存储在内存和带宽可能有限的客户端上存储页和控件的状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-110">For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister> class stores page and controls' state on the Web server, instead of the client, to decrease the amount of information that must be sent and stored on a client that has potentially limited memory and bandwidth.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="51614-111">"_VIEWSTATE"的最大大小`<hidden>`可以通过设置 HTML 元素<xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A>属性或通过<xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A>配置设置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-111">The maximum size of the "_VIEWSTATE" `<hidden>` HTML element can be set through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> property or through the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> configuration setting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="51614-112">当设置此值，并且"_VIEWSTATE"元素的长度将超过最大长度时，将内容划分为多个"_VIEWSTATE"元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51614-112">When this value is set and the length of the "_VIEWSTATE" element would exceed the maximum length, the content is divided into multiple "_VIEWSTATE" elements.</span></span>  
  
   
  
